[Java] Class SetFromLiveMap

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Set, java.io.Serializable
public class SetFromLiveMap
extends java.util.AbstractSet

Creates a Set backed by a given map (using the map's java.util.Map#keySet() for the contents of the set).

As java.util.Collections#newSetFromMap(java.util.Map) and guava's Sets#newSetFromMap(Map)#newSetFromMap(Map), but accepts a non-empty map. Also supports others modifying the backing map simultaneously, if the backing map is a ConcurrentMap.
